{"author":{"id":"bd295dc777972a8e4c3c7232dd9b961cc225e5d1372df7df743ab1f395854fa9"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1669635661,"nonce":"iOZm8mQ6Vvtxlc0aFfXQz6fhTts=","metadata":{"github-id":"IC_kwDOCGKeh85PNfMh","github-url":"https://github.com/git-bug/git-bug/issues/929#issuecomment-1328935713"},"message":"\u003e I'm also on Arch Linux and experienced the same issue. I solved it like this:\n\u003e \n\u003e ```shell\n\u003e $ for keytype in rsa ecdsa ed25519; do\n\u003e     ssh-keyscan -t \"$keytype\" github.com \u003e\u003e ~/.ssh/known_hosts\n\u003e   done\n\u003e $ \n\u003e ```\n\nThanks, this solved the issue for me!","files":null}]}